name: Airborne G-13
description: With a hint of sage & lemon, this relaxing strain tastes just like it smells. The rumored government strain “G-13” crossed with Northern Lights #2 create an enjoyable indica dominant strain.

name: Blue Dream
description: Good Chemistry’s award-winning strain, Blue Dream, is a sweet, smooth, smoke and may promote creativity. Known for it’s strength and length of high, Blue Dream’s lineage may balance full body relief with cerebral stimulation.

name: Chemdawg
description: With the rumored celebrity parents of OG Kush & Sour Diesel, this sativa dominant strain is a favorite amongst cannabis connoisseurs. Chemdawg is a potent strain that has a strong diesel-like aroma. Consumers may expect a creative lift accompanied by a relieving sensation.
